e used in decision-making.'),(17,3,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','105.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(18,3,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','7.5','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(19,3,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','135.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(20,4,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','100.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(21,4,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','7.5','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(22,4,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','125.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(23,4,'Cambridge English','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','191.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(24,4,'iTEP','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','4.5','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(25,4,'SAT/ACT',NULL,'Optional',NULL,'Not required but may be submitted for context.'),(26,4,'Transcript',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Official high school transcript is required.'),(27,4,'Essay',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Personal essay is required as part of the application.'),(28,5,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','100.0','A score of 100 or above on the 120-point scale is competitive, with sub-scores above 24 required.'),(29,5,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','7.5','A score of 7.5 or above on the IELTS is competitive.'),(30,5,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','135.0','A score of 135 or higher on the Duolingo English Test is competitive.'),(31,5,'SAT/ACT',NULL,'Optional',NULL,'UCLA will not consider SAT or ACT scores for admission or scholarship purposes.'),(32,5,'Transcript','Quantity required','Required',NULL,'Secondary school records and official records from colleges or universities attended are required.'),(33,5,'English-as-a-Second-Language Placement Examination (ESLPE)',NULL,'Conditionally Required',NULL,'Required for admitted students whose native language is not English to assess English proficiency.'),(34,6,'Common Application',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Submitted as part of the application.'),(35,6,'High School Transcript',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Must be official copies submitted by a school official.'),(36,6,'Senior Year Grades',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Must be submitted when available according to the decision timeframe.'),(37,6,'Counselor Recommendation',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Must include the School Report form.'),(38,6,'Teacher Evaluation',NULL,'Required',NULL,'Must be submitted by a teacher.'),(39,6,'Standardized Tests',NULL,'Optional',NULL,'BU is test optional for first-year applicants until spring 2029.'),(40,6,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','90.0','If English is not the applicant\'s first language, competitive total score is 90-100, with at least 20 in each section.'),(41,6,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','7.0','A total score of 7 or higher is required.'),(42,6,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','125.0','Competitive total score for the Duolingo English Test is 125-135.'),(43,7,'Transcript','Quantity required','Required',NULL,'Applicants must self-report their grades honestly and accurately.'),(44,7,'Letters of Recommendation','Quantity required','Optional','2.0','Select applicants may be invited to submit up to two letters of recommendation.'),(45,7,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','100.0','Competitive score for non-native English speakers.'),(46,7,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','7.0','Overall band score is considered for non-native English speakers.'),(47,7,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','120.0','Acceptable alternative for non-native English speakers.'),(48,7,'PTE','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','68.0','Alternative English test required for non-native speakers.'),(49,7,'Cambridge English','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required',NULL,'Scores accepted, specific scores not listed.'),(50,7,'iTEP','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required',NULL,'Scores accepted, specific scores not listed.'),(51,8,'TOEFL','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','83.0','Minimum score required for TOEFL.'),(52,8,'IELTS','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','7.0','Minimum score required for IELTS.'),(53,8,'Duolingo','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','115.0','Minimum score required for Duolingo.'),(54,8,'GPA','Minimum GPA','Required','3.0','California residents must earn a GPA of 3.0 (or better) with no grade lower than \'C\'. Non-California residents must earn a GPA of 3.4 (or better) with no grade lower than \'C\'.'),(55,8,'High School Diploma','Quantity required','Required','1.0','Must have completed secondary school with a superior average in academic subjects.'),(56,9,'SAT','Minimum Score','Required','600.0','Minimum score required for the Evidence-based Reading and Writing section.'),(57,9,'ACT','Minimum Score','Required','26.0','Minimum score required on the English section.'),(58,9,'TOEFL','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','88.0','Minimum score for exams taken before January 21, 2026.'),(59,9,'TOEFL','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','4.5','Minimum score for exams taken on or after January 21, 2026.'),(60,9,'IELTS','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','6.5','Minimum score required, with at least 6.0 in each section.'),(61,9,'Duolingo','Minimum Score','Conditionally Required','115.0','Generally, applicants have a 110 or higher in all individual subscores.'),(62,10,'TOEFL','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','80.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(63,10,'IELTS','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','6.5','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(64,10,'Duolingo','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','105.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(65,10,'PTE','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','53.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(66,10,'Cambridge English','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','169.0','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.'),(67,10,'iTEP','Competitive Score','Conditionally Required','3.7','No strict minimum, but this is the competitive score.');
